actions.message:
**Welcome to the rules channel! Please familiarize yourself with the following rules. Failing to abide will result in a punishment.**

1:  Spamming will not be tolerated, if you spam you will be warned/muted, this includes spamming bot commands.

2: Be respectful to all users regardless of your grudges in the server.

3:  Use each channel for its designated purpose. Each channels' name is self explanatory, though most conversations are allowed in main chat.

4:  Racial slurs are prohibited. Your message will be deleted and you will receive escalating punishments. 

5: Listen to staff. Any form of harassment towards staff is unacceptable. 

6: Please, don't impersonate anyone. Especially staff members.

7:  Do not advertise. As staff, we do not tolerate advertising of ANY kind  here.

8:  Don't abuse bugs, if you find a bug please report to staff.

9: Do not react to posts with "KYS" this will result in a high punishment.

10: IP grabbing, doxxing, or leaking personal information of others will not be tolerated.

11: Discrimination of any kind. This includes racism and sexism. Also, we are not a dating service.

12:  Use common sense together with everything above, if you think something is stupid and against the rules, it most likely is.

13: Bypassing our punishment system is not allowed.

14: Talking about all the related things about cracking/checking accounts either cracking softwares will not be tolerated.

15: Swearing is ALLOWED but keep it in minimal

16: Tagging the alerts role with result in a permanent ban
[@here]
